It would be helpful if users could attach updated files with an existing filename.  For example, I like to name my own file revisions like filename_yyyymmdd.ext, and if I uploaded each revision, it would create a new file listing instead of tracking revisions to the same file.  I'd like to be able to attach files with different names to the same file revision tree.

